HEADWORD: nuclear fusion
<hw>nuclear fusion</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A type of nuclear reaction in
which atomic nuclei combine to form more massive nuclei with the
simultaneous release of energy.</def> <syn><b>Syn. --</b> fusion,
nuclear fusion reaction.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

